うん？

138
00:09:57.722 --> 00:10:01.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（ルフィ）
何も見捨てられねえから
いっつも苦しんでる

139
00:10:01.642 --> 00:10:05.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
この反乱でも
誰も死ななきゃいいと思ってる

140
00:10:05.354 --> 00:10:07.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
誰も死なねえ…

141
00:10:07.773 --> 00:10:11.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
よくいるな
そういう甘ったるい平和バカは

142
00:10:12.069 --> 00:10:14.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
本当の戦いを知らねえからだ

143
00:10:15.197 --> 00:10:17.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
お前も そう思うだろ

144
00:10:17.575 --> 00:10:18.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うん

145
00:10:27.126 --> 00:10:28.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
だけど あいつは―

146
00:10:28.586 --> 00:10:32.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
お前がいる限り 死ぬまで
お前に向かっていくから

147
00:10:34.884 --> 00:10:37.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
俺が ここでしとめるんだ！

148
00:10:38.054 --> 00:10:41.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
フフフフッ ハハハッ

149
00:10:41.474 --> 00:10:42.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
くだらなすぎるぜ

150
00:10:43.643 --> 00:10:47.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
救えねえバカは てめえだな
これがいい例だ

151
00:10:48.022 --> 00:10:51.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
他人となれ合っちまったがために
死んでゆく

152
00:10:51.942 --> 00:10:56.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
そういうやつらを
俺は ごまんと見捨ててきたぜ

153
00:10:56.530 --> 00:10:57.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ルフィ）ヘエ…

154
00:10:57.907 --> 00:10:58.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
じゃあ―

155
00:10:59.325 --> 00:11:01.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
おめえがバカじゃねえのか
（関節を鳴らす音）

156
00:11:03.954 --> 00:11:06.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
フフフフ…

157
00:11:06.457 --> 00:11:08.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
何がおかしい

158
00:11:08.876 --> 00:11:11.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
てめえも死ぬか？ ニコ･ロビン

159
00:11:12.254 --> 00:11:14.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
その気ならば お好きに

160
00:11:14.632 --> 00:11:17.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
それに その名は
呼ばない約束でしょ

161
00:11:17.843 --> 00:11:19.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（クロコダイル）どこへ行く？

162
00:11:19.512 --> 00:11:21.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ミス･オールサンデー）
アルバーナへ先に行ってるわ

163
00:11:22.723 --> 00:11:24.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
つかめねえ女だぜ

164
00:11:28.562 --> 00:11:30.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
３分やろう

165
00:11:33.776 --> 00:11:35.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
それ以上―

166
00:11:35.986 --> 00:11:38.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
てめえの相手なんぞ
してられねえ

167
00:11:58.217 --> 00:12:05.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（風の音）

168
00:12:21.824 --> 00:12:23.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
３分やろう

169
00:12:23.909 --> 00:12:27.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
それ以上 てめえの相手なんぞ
してられねえ

170
00:12:34.920 --> 00:12:36.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
文句でも？

171
00:12:37.715 --> 00:12:39.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ルフィ）いや いいぞ
（関節を鳴らす音）

172
00:12:40.968 --> 00:12:42.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ゴムゴムの…

173
00:12:42.261 --> 00:12:42.887 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うん？

174
00:12:43.012 --> 00:12:44.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ピストル！

175
00:12:46.932 --> 00:12:47.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ぬうっ

176
00:12:53.981 --> 00:12:55.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（クロコダイル）フンッ
（ルフィ）うおっ

177
00:12:55.691 --> 00:12:56.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（クロコダイル）ほう

178
00:12:56.942 --> 00:12:58.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ゴムゴムの―

179
00:12:59.403 --> 00:13:00.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
スタンプ！

180
00:13:02.781 --> 00:13:04.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ぐぐぐぐ…

181
00:13:05.201 --> 00:13:06.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うわっ

182
00:13:11.540 --> 00:13:14.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
１つだけ 言っておくぞ
麦わらのルフィ

183
00:13:14.668 --> 00:13:19.089 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
どう あがこうとも
お前じゃ 絶対に俺は…

184
00:13:19.215 --> 00:13:23.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ゴムゴムのガトリング！

185
00:13:23.135 --> 00:13:26.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
オリャリャリャリャリャ…

186
00:13:30.392 --> 00:13:32.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（荒い息）

187
00:13:34.813 --> 00:13:36.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
フフフフフフッ

188
00:13:37.775 --> 00:13:39.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（荒い息）

189
00:13:39.818 --> 00:13:42.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
いいか 麦わらのルフィ

190
00:13:42.363 --> 00:13:46.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
こんな蚊のような攻撃を
いつまで続けようとも―

191
00:13:46.825 --> 00:13:50.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
決してお前は俺に…
（ルフィ）ゴムゴムの…

192
00:13:50.162 --> 00:13:52.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
バズーカ！

193
00:13:53.249 --> 00:13:54.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うぬっ

194
00:13:55.501 --> 00:13:56.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
んぐっ

195
00:13:56.710 --> 00:14:00.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
オノ！

196
00:14:07.513 --> 00:14:11.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（荒い息）

197
00:14:11.475 --> 00:14:16.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
このっ このこのっ
潰れたか この砂ワニ！

198
00:14:19.149 --> 00:14:20.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ムダだと言ってるんだ

199
00:14:20.943 --> 00:14:21.986 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ルフィ）なっ…

200
00:14:22.570 --> 00:14:23.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
この野郎

201
00:14:24.029 --> 00:14:27.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
貴様のようなゴム人間が
どうあがこうとも―

202
00:14:27.867 --> 00:14:30.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
この俺には絶対に…

203
00:14:30.202 --> 00:14:30.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ぐっ

204
00:14:31.412 --> 00:14:32.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（クロコダイル）勝(か)ぺ…

205
00:14:33.831 --> 00:14:34.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
かぺ？

206
00:14:35.040 --> 00:14:37.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
おめえ 何が言いてえんだ
さっきから

207
00:14:37.251 --> 00:14:39.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（クロコダイル）ううっ…

208
00:14:46.468 --> 00:14:49.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
もう遊びは この辺でよかろう

209
00:14:50.931 --> 00:14:52.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
麦わらのルフィ

210
00:14:52.808 --> 00:14:55.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
俺は ずっと
真面目にやってるぞ

211
00:14:56.437 --> 00:15:00.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
でも まいったなあ
全然 殴れねえや あいつ

212
00:15:00.274 --> 00:15:02.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
サラサラしやがって

213
00:15:02.151 --> 00:15:06.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
俺とお前では
海賊の格が違うんだ

214
00:15:06.906 --> 00:15:08.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
デザート･スパーダ！

215
00:15:10.075 --> 00:15:10.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おっ

216
00:15:11.952 --> 00:15:12.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（岩が斬れる音）
（ルフィ）いっ

217
00:15:18.250 --> 00:15:20.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
いっ ぎぎ…

218
00:15:20.210 --> 00:15:22.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（クロコダイル）いい見極めだ

219
00:15:22.546 --> 00:15:25.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
受けてりゃ “痛(いて)え”じゃ
済まなかったぜ

220
00:15:27.509 --> 00:15:30.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
何だ？ 砂漠が割れたぞ

221
00:15:30.721 --> 00:15:32.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
悪魔の実の能力は―

222
00:15:32.264 --> 00:15:37.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
使い方と訓練次第で
いくらでも強い戦闘手段になる

223
00:15:37.853 --> 00:15:42.066 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
能力だけに かまけた
そこらのバカとは 俺は違うぞ

224
00:15:42.900 --> 00:15:47.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
この俺に盾ついたことを
存分に後悔するんだな

225
00:15:50.824 --> 00:15:53.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
デザート･ジラソーレ！

226
00:15:58.082 --> 00:15:58.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
わあっ

227
00:16:05.130 --> 00:16:07.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
何だ？ 何だ 何だ 何だ？

228
00:16:08.092 --> 00:16:13.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（慌てる声）

229
00:16:13.847 --> 00:16:17.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
砂が地面に吸い込まれてく！

230
00:16:17.810 --> 00:16:20.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うわっ うわっ うわあっ

231
00:16:20.771 --> 00:16:23.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（慌てる声）

232
00:16:24.233 --> 00:16:26.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（クロコダイル）
流砂を知らんのか

233
00:16:27.027 --> 00:16:31.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
墓標の要らねえ
砂漠の便利な棺桶(かんおけ)さ

234
00:16:31.448 --> 00:16:35.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
地下の水脈に
砂が引きずり込まれるんだ

235
00:16:35.786 --> 00:16:38.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
その位置くらい 俺は感知できる

236
00:16:38.455 --> 00:16:39.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
わーっ！

237
00:16:39.331 --> 00:16:43.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
砂漠の戦闘で この俺に
かなう者は この世にいない

238
00:16:43.585 --> 00:16:46.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ルフィの慌てる声）

239
00:16:46.505 --> 00:16:47.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
砂なんかに…

240
00:16:47.840 --> 00:16:49.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うえっ ハア ハア…

241
00:16:49.508 --> 00:16:52.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
生き埋めにされてたまるか！

242
00:16:54.263 --> 00:16:55.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
この野郎

243
00:16:56.015 --> 00:16:57.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ゴムゴムの―

244
00:16:58.100 --> 00:16:59.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
バズーカ！

245
00:17:01.437 --> 00:17:04.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
殴って効かねえんなら
まず取っ捕まえてやる

246
00:17:04.898 --> 00:17:07.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ゴムゴムの網！

247
00:17:09.695 --> 00:17:10.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うわっ

248
00:17:10.529 --> 00:17:14.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
学習できんのか？ てめえは
ムダなんだよ

249
00:17:15.117 --> 00:17:18.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ゴムゴムのムチ！

250
00:17:20.622 --> 00:17:22.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
まだ繰り返す気か

251
00:17:23.709 --> 00:17:26.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
うわっ がっ ああっ
離せ この野郎！

252
00:17:27.337 --> 00:17:28.047 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
バルハン！

253
00:17:28.630 --> 00:17:31.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ルフィ）
うわっ うっ うっ…

254
00:17:32.885 --> 00:17:35.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ああっ う… 腕が…

255
00:17:39.183 --> 00:17:42.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うわあああっ 腕が… 腕が…

256
00:17:42.978 --> 00:17:46.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ミイラになった！
腕がミイラに…

257
00:17:46.190 --> 00:17:48.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（クロコダイル）砂だからな

258
00:17:48.317 --> 00:17:51.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
お前の腕の水分を
吸収しちまったのさ

259
00:17:52.196 --> 00:17:54.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
そうやって
全身の水分を絞り出し―

260
00:17:54.907 --> 00:17:57.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
干からびて死ぬのもよかろう

261
00:17:58.202 --> 00:18:00.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
砂漠の情緒があってな

262
00:18:00.871 --> 00:18:02.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（荒い息）

263
00:18:02.331 --> 00:18:03.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
じ… 冗談じゃねえ

264
00:18:04.833 --> 00:18:07.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あっ そうだ　水！

265
00:18:07.711 --> 00:18:08.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うん？

266
00:18:12.674 --> 00:18:13.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
んんっ

267
00:18:14.176 --> 00:18:15.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
くだらん

268
00:18:15.844 --> 00:18:17.262 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
くだらんことねえぞ

269
00:18:17.596 --> 00:18:20.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
この水はな ユバの
カラカラのおっさんが―

270
00:18:20.474 --> 00:18:23.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
一晩かけて
作ってくれた水なんだ

271
00:18:23.268 --> 00:18:26.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（トト）
ルフィ君
これを持っていきなさい

272
00:18:26.563 --> 00:18:28.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
言ってたぞ おっさんだって

273
00:18:31.151 --> 00:18:34.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ユバは 砂なんかには
負けやしねえって

274
00:18:34.238 --> 00:18:36.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ゴムゴムの…

275
00:18:36.615 --> 00:18:38.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
まだ やる気か

276
00:18:38.951 --> 00:18:40.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ルフィ）バクバク！

277
00:18:46.458 --> 00:18:49.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
くだらねえマネするんじゃねえ

278
00:18:50.671 --> 00:18:52.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ルフィのせき込み）

279
00:18:53.298 --> 00:18:54.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
死ね

280
00:18:54.591 --> 00:18:58.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
その たくましい
ユバの大地と共によ

281
00:18:58.804 --> 00:19:00.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ゲホッ ああ？

282
00:19:00.472 --> 00:19:04.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（クロコダイル）
３分を経過した
最初に言ったな

283
00:19:04.768 --> 00:19:07.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
これ以上 お前に
付き合ってる暇はない

284
00:19:08.605 --> 00:19:10.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
サーブルス

285
00:19:21.660 --> 00:19:23.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ルフィ）うわあっ

286
00:19:27.082 --> 00:19:29.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
いい砂の乾き具合だ

287
00:19:30.377 --> 00:19:32.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（町の人）
砂嵐だ
南の空に砂嵐が見える

288
00:19:33.130 --> 00:19:33.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
避難しろ

289
00:19:34.006 --> 00:19:37.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（町の人）
待て 砂嵐は来ないぞ
そのまま南へ向かっている

290
00:19:38.051 --> 00:19:40.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（たしぎ）
スモーカー大佐 あれ…

291
00:19:46.518 --> 00:19:48.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ウソップ）
ビビ どうした？

292
00:19:48.395 --> 00:19:50.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ビビ）
レインベースの方角に砂嵐が

293
00:19:50.772 --> 00:19:51.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ナミ）えっ…

294
00:19:52.608 --> 00:19:53.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あいつだわ

295
00:19:57.487 --> 00:19:58.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ルフィ…

296
00:20:06.747 --> 00:20:08.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（クロコダイル）
いいか 麦わらのルフィ

297
00:20:09.208 --> 00:20:13.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ここらの卓越風は
常に北から南へ吹いている

298
00:20:13.962 --> 00:20:16.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
もしも この砂嵐の子供が―

299
00:20:16.882 --> 00:20:21.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
そいつに乗って
成長しながら南へ下っていくと―

300
00:20:21.303 --> 00:20:24.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
でかくなった砂嵐は
どこへ ぶつかると思う？

301
00:20:24.765 --> 00:20:27.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あっ 南って…

302
00:20:28.644 --> 00:20:30.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ユバさ

303
00:20:31.980 --> 00:20:34.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
な… なんで！

304
00:20:36.109 --> 00:20:38.820 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
お前 何やってんだ やめろ！

305
00:20:39.947 --> 00:20:43.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
見ろ 少しずつ南下し始めた

306
00:20:43.617 --> 00:20:46.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
カラカラのおっさんには
関係ねえだろうが

307
00:20:47.537 --> 00:20:50.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
この！ 止まれ このっ

308
00:20:51.375 --> 00:20:53.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
止まれ この野郎 止まれ！

309
00:20:54.753 --> 00:20:56.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うわっ

310
00:20:56.380 --> 00:20:59.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（クロコダイル）
フフフッ ムダだ やめとけ

311
00:21:00.217 --> 00:21:02.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
その砂嵐は風力を増し―

312
00:21:02.886 --> 00:21:06.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
この俺でさえ
止めようのねえ風速を得る

313
00:21:06.890 --> 00:21:08.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ふざけんな お前

314
00:21:09.810 --> 00:21:11.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ユバは終わりだ

315
00:21:11.812 --> 00:21:13.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
止めろよ 今すぐ

316
00:21:13.897 --> 00:21:15.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
と…

317
00:21:27.703 --> 00:21:30.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（クロコダイル）
この俺を誰だと思ってる

318
00:21:30.706 --> 00:21:36.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（血が滴る音）

319
00:21:37.421 --> 00:21:41.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（クロコダイル）
てめえのような
口先だけのルーキーなんざ

320
00:21:41.633 --> 00:21:46.805 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
いくらでもいるぜ
麦わらのルフィ

321
00:21:47.889 --> 00:21:51.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
このグランドラインにゃあよ

322
00:21:51.643 --> 00:21:54.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（砂嵐の音）

323
00:21:54.604 --> 00:22:00.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
♪～

324
00:22:59.544 --> 00:23:05.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
～♪

325
00:23:10.847 --> 00:23:13.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（ウソップ）
何！ このカニで
川は渡れねえか

326
00:23:13.183 --> 00:23:15.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（ビビ）
砂漠の生き物だから
水は苦手なの

327
00:23:15.644 --> 00:23:17.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（ウソップ）
でも カニだろうが
何とかしろ

328
00:23:17.145 --> 00:23:18.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ナミ）
何とかして ハサミくーん

329
00:23:19.147 --> 00:23:21.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（チョッパー）
そうだ
ハサミは踊り子が大好きだ

330
00:23:21.358 --> 00:23:22.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ナミ）これでいいの？

331
00:23:22.275 --> 00:23:23.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（マツゲ･サンジ）ブルルルッ

332
00:23:23.652 --> 00:23:25.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ゾロ）
余計なのも壊れてんぞ

333
00:23:25.821 --> 00:23:26.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ルフィ）
次回 ワンピース

334
00:23:27.114 --> 00:23:29.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
「奇跡への疾走！
アラバスタ動物ランド」

335
00:23:30.117 --> 00:23:32.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
海賊王に 俺はなる！

